    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#projects" class="px-8 py-3 bg-violet-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-violet-500 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-violet-500/20">
        View Work
      </a>
      <a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-violet-500 text-violet-400 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-violet-600 hover:border-violet-600 hover:text-white transition-colors">
